Tremmer:

* There were fewer things to hit in this fight but the movement off to the 
side caught his senses, the smell of fresh mech-fluid aware to his senses.
By the scent alone he could tell that it was a female, grown.  But also 
there was some sort of force, almost like the slightest of pressure he felt 
against his mole skin.  There was something special about that woman.
So with that Tremmer started to approach the place where she would be, 
transforming into Robot mode.*

" Er...ev'rything right 'ere?"

........................................

Biomass, Nue'e:

* Transforming into beast mode, Biomass sighed and leaned his elongated head 
on one of his two longest tenticles.*

" Some research we're doing."

* Nue'e smiled.*

" Well, if we would have gone to that battle at the other base, where 
Sablime was going to, we could see how they fought."

* Biomass looked down at Nue'e with one large, dark eye.*

" We could still go."

* Nue'e nodded and slipped into the water, turning into seahorse mode and 
waited for Biomass.
He went in after her, and soon they both disappeared into the depths.*

.........................................

Desmonus:

* Positioning herself infront of a window, Desmonus leaned down, set her 
elbow against the sill and leaned her head on her palm.
Life was dull.
Of course, to see a fem like her bending in the middle of the hall to look 
out of a window...wasn't an every day thing.*

.........................................

Sublime:

* Deciding to stay out of the battle, she stood off to the side.*
